OL,6,FA private mental health care provider
OL,7,Fhas been fined #650,000, after the
OL,8,Fdeath of a patient who escaped
OL,9,Fhospital, climbed over a fence and was
OL,10,Fhit by a train in
OL,12,FPersonal trainer after being
OL,13,F"inappropriately unattended" for
OL,14,Fseveral minutes in September 2020, an
OL,15,Finquest jury ruled in 2022.
