OL,6,FPriory Healthcare Ltd admitted
OL,7,Fbreaching the 2008 Health and Social
OL,8,FCare Act at Birmingham Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt on Friday, by failing to provide
OL,10,Fsafe care and treatment "resulting in
OL,11,FMatthew Caseby and other service users
OL,12,Fbeing exposed to a significant risk of
OL,13,Favoidable harm".
OL,15,FAn inquest held in April 2022 was told
OL,16,FMr Caseby was able to leave the
OL,17,Fhospital, where he was an NHS-funded
OL,18,Fpatient, by climbing over a 2.3-metre-
OL,19,Fhigh courtyard fence.
