OL,6,FThe inquest jury, which heard the
OL,7,FUniversity of Birmingham graduate
OL,8,Fshould have been under constant
OL,9,Fobservation but was left unattended,
OL,10,Freached a conclusion that death "was
OL,11,Fcontributed to by neglect".
OL,13,FFollowing the verdict, Birmingham and
OL,14,FSolihull senior coroner Louise Hunt
OL,15,Furged health chiefs to consider
OL,16,Fimposing minimum standards for
OL,17,Fperimeter fences at acute mental
OL,18,Fhealth units.
