OL,6,FMr Caseby, who lived in London, was
OL,7,Foriginally detained under the Mental
OL,8,FHealth Act following reports of a man
OL,9,Frunning on to railway tracks near
OL,10,FOxford five days before his death.
OL,12,FOpening the case against Priory
OL,13,FHealthcare at the magistrates' court
OL,14,Fhearing, CQC barrister James Marsland
OL,15,Fsaid other patients had absconded from
OL,16,Fthe ward on previous occasions.
