OL,6,FMitigating for Priory Healthcare,
OL,7,Fwhose chief executive Rebekah
OL,8,FCresswell attended the court hearing,
OL,9,FMr Greaney said: "It should be
OL,10,Fpublicly understood that the company
OL,11,Fhas not admitted any charge alleging
OL,12,Fit caused Mr Caseby's death."
OL,14,FThe defence lawyer added that the
OL,15,Fcompany had pleaded guilty on the
OL,16,Fbasis that it had exposed service
OL,17,Fusers to a risk of avoidable harm by
OL,18,Fnot carrying out a full review of
OL,19,Fthree previous abscondments from the
OL,20,Fward, not all of which took place over
OL,21,Fthe same fence.
