OL,6,FThe first two of three incidents in
OL,7,F2018, 2019 and 2020 saw patients
OL,8,Fsuffer no injury.
OL,10,FBut the third incident on July 17 2020
OL,11,Fsaw a male patient, who visited a
OL,12,Fsupermarket, suffering a cut to the
OL,13,Fleg.
OL,15,FAt the time of the incident there was
OL,16,F"no industry standard or guidance" on
OL,17,Fminimum fencing height for outdoor
OL,18,Fspace attached to wards of the type
OL,19,Finvolved, Mr Greaney told the court.
