OL,6,FStressing that Priory Healthcare was
OL,7,Fmaking efforts to tackle the problem
OL,8,Fof patients absconding, Mr Greaney
OL,9,Fadded: "It is a fact that the company
OL,10,Fwas working hard to address the issue.
OL,12,F"It certainly was not a company that
OL,13,Fdidn't care."
OL,15,FLessons had been learned, Mr Greaney
OL,16,Fsaid, as part of a continuing drive to
OL,17,Fensure patient safety, while the fence
OL,18,Fheight had been twice raised and anti-
OL,19,Fclimb roller-bars have been installed.
