OL,6,FDistrict Judge Shamim Qureshi said
OL,7,Fdealing with patients detained under
OL,8,Fthe Mental Health Act was a very
OL,9,Fdifficult area for care providers.
OL,11,FThe judge, who also made an order for
OL,12,Fprosecution costs of more than
OL,13,F#43,000, said the company had to care
OL,14,Ffor patients "who are vulnerable and
OL,15,Fneed protection from themselves".
OL,17,FHe said the firm's culpability was
OL,18,Fhigh and the risk of harm posed by the
OL,19,Foffence had been in the medium
OL,20,Fcategory under the sentencing
OL,21,Fguidelines.
